    Get recent trades

    market_recent_trades.Rd

    Exposes the GET /api/v3/trades endpoint.

    market_recent_trades(symbol)

    Arguments

    symbol

    Symbol.

    Value

    A data frame.

    Examples

    market_recent_trades("BTCUSDT")
